Developer Terms of Use
des:
Book suggestions is a easy to use alexa skill that helps you find book suggestions and reads you their blurbs.

Please note that we currently have the winner for each category on the skill but are looking to add the runner-ups sometime in the future.

Before you submit a negative review, be sure to email us at voice@techie.com for assistance and suggestions.
